data.description: Welcome home, to this spacious and well maintained 5/3.5/2 home in desirable East Meadow subdivision. Primary Bedroom and Bath located on the 1st floor. 4 extra bedrooms upstairs with 2 full bathrooms and a large game room. Tile floors in all the wet areas and granite counters with tile backsplash in the kitchen. Kitchen is open to the family room which is perfect for entertaining. Covered patio out back with an extended slab. Upstairs attic is not only decked but has shelving that makes storage easier. Close to shopping and restaurants for your convenience. Don't delay schedule showing today.
